==Stenson Award==
{{see also|Arizona Fall League#Stenson Award}}
The Stenson Award was created in 2004 by the Arizona Fall League, in memory of Dernell Stenson,<ref>[http://www.baseball-almanac.com/players/player.php?p=stensde01 Dernell Stenson Stats]. Baseball Almanac website. Retrieved 2010-12-31.</ref> a Scorpions outfielder (Cincinnati Reds), who was killed in a carjacking on November 5, 2003.<ref>[http://www.baseball-almanac.com/awards/stenson_award.shtml Stenson Award]. Baseball Almanac website. Retrieved 2010-12-31.</ref>

